<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Branch PCI Compliance — Deployment Guide</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:          #f7f6f2;
  --bg2:         #efede7;
  --surface:     #ffffff;
  --border:      #ddd9d0;
  --border2:     #c8c3b8;
  --text:        #1a1916;
  --text2:       #4a4742;
  --text3:       #7a7570;
  --mono:        'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  --sans:        'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;

  /* Input color coding */
  --c-required:  #1bc47d;
  --c-req-bg:    #edfaf3;
  --c-req-b:     #a0dfc0;

  --c-aws:       #d35400;
  --c-aws-bg:    #fef5ec;
  --c-aws-b:     #f5d5b0;

  --c-gcp:       #1a73e8;
  --c-gcp-bg:    #eef4fd;
  --c-gcp-b:     #b8d0f5;

  --c-cf:        #f48024;
  --c-cf-bg:     #fff8f0;
  --c-cf-b:      #fad5a0;

  --c-drata:     #6b3fa0;
  --c-drata-bg:  #f5f0fc;
  --c-drata-b:   #d4b8f0;

  --c-github:    #24292f;
  --c-github-bg: #f0f0f0;
  --c-github-b:  #c0c0c0;

  --c-optional:  #2e7d32;
  --c-opt-bg:    #f0faf1;
  --c-opt-b:     #a8d5ab;

  --step-done:   #1bc47d;
  --step-active: #1bc47d;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── Layout ─────────────────────────────────── */
.layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* ── Sidebar ─────────────────────────────────── */
aside {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  height: 100vh;
  overflow-y: auto;
  background: var(--surface);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 2rem 0;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.sidebar-brand {
  padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.brand-label {
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}

.brand-title {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.sidebar-section-label {
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}

nav a {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  padding: 0.45rem 1.5rem;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--text2);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

nav a:hover {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
}

nav a.active {
  border-left-color: #0d7a4e;
  background: #edfaf3;
  color: #0d7a4e;
  font-weight: 500;
}

nav a .step-circle {
  width: 18px; height: 18px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text3);
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* Legend */
.legend {
  margin: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0;
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.legend-title {
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.legend-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--text2);
}

.swatch {
  width: 12px; height: 12px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ── Main content ─────────────────────────────── */
main {
  padding: 0;
  max-width: 900px;
}

/* ── Page header ─────────────────────────────── */
.page-header {
  padding: 3rem 3rem 2.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--surface);
}

.page-eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #0d7a4e;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  font-family: var(--mono);
}

.page-title {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.page-desc {
  color: var(--text2);
  max-width: 600px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

/* ── Step sections ───────────────────────────── */
.step {
  padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.step-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
}

.step-num-large {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--text);
  color: #fff;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.step-title-block {}

.step-phase {
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  font-family: var(--mono);
}

.step-title {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.step-desc {
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

/* ── Sub-steps ─────────────────────────────── */
.substep {
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
}

.substep-title {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.substep-title .badge {
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  padding: 0.15em 0.5em;
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ── Code blocks ─────────────────────────────── */
.code-block {
  background: #0a120d;
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 0.75rem 0;
  border: 1px solid #333;
}

.code-label {
  background: #0f1e14;
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #5a8a6a;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  border-bottom: 1px solid #1a3522;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

.code-label .copy-btn {
  background: none;
  border: 1px solid #2a5038;
  color: #5a8a6a;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
  border-radius: 3px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  transition: all 0.15s;
}

.code-label .copy-btn:hover {
  border-color: #5a8a6a;
  color: #ccc;
}

.code-label .copy-btn.copied {
  border-color: var(--c-optional);
  color: #4caf50;
}

pre {
  padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
  overflow-x: auto;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: #bddece;
}

/* Syntax color classes */
.c  { color: #5a8a6a; font-style: italic; }           /* comment */
.k  { color: #f5a623; }                            /* keyword */
.s  { color: #1bc47d; }                            /* string */
.n  { color: #bddece; }                            /* normal */
.p  { color: #8ab89a; }                               /* punctuation */

/* Input color tokens — inline highlight */
.i-req    { color: #ff7b72; background: rgba(192,57,43,0.15); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }
.i-aws    { color: #ffa657; background: rgba(211,84,0,0.15);  border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }
.i-gcp    { color: #79c0ff; background: rgba(26,115,232,0.15); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }
.i-cf     { color: #ffb86c; background: rgba(244,128,36,0.15); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }
.i-drata  { color: #d2a8ff; background: rgba(107,63,160,0.15); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }
.i-gh     { color: #a8daff; background: rgba(36,41,47,0.35);   border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }
.i-opt    { color: #7ee787; background: rgba(46,125,50,0.15);  border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }

/* ── Input tables ────────────────────────────── */
.input-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 0.75rem 0;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
}

.input-table thead tr {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.input-table th {
  padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text3);
  text-align: left;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.input-table td {
  padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  vertical-align: top;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.input-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

.input-table .key {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text);
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.input-table .desc {
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
}

.input-table .where {
  color: var(--text3);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
}

/* Colored row backgrounds */
.row-req    { background: #edfaf3; border-left: 3px solid #1bc47d !important; }
.row-aws    { background: var(--c-aws-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--c-aws) !important; }
.row-gcp    { background: var(--c-gcp-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--c-gcp) !important; }
.row-cf     { background: var(--c-cf-bg);  border-left: 3px solid var(--c-cf) !important; }
.row-drata  { background: var(--c-drata-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--c-drata) !important; }
.row-gh     { background: var(--c-github-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--c-github) !important; }
.row-opt    { background: var(--c-opt-bg); border-left: 3px solid var(--c-optional) !important; }

/* ── Callouts ────────────────────────────────── */
.callout {
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin: 0.75rem 0;
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.callout-icon { font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.05rem; }
.callout-body { flex: 1; }
.callout-body strong { font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }

.callout-warn { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #f5d87a; color: #5c4a00; }
.callout-info { background: #eef4fd; border: 1px solid var(--c-gcp-b); color: #0d47a1; }
.callout-tip  { background: var(--c-opt-bg); border: 1px solid var(--c-opt-b); color: #1b5e20; }
.callout-danger { background: #edfaf3; border: 1px solid #a0dfc0; color: #7f0000; }

/* ── Checklist ───────────────────────────────── */
.checklist {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0.75rem 0;
}

.checklist li {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.7rem;
  padding: 0.5rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--text2);
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.check-box {
  width: 16px; height: 16px;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 3px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}

.checklist li .tag-provider {
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  padding: 0.1em 0.45em;
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 2px;
}

/* ── Pill badges ─────────────────────────────── */
.pill {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  padding: 0.2em 0.55em;
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  vertical-align: middle;
}

.pill-req   { background: #edfaf3;   color: #0d7a4e; border: 1px solid #a0dfc0; }
.pill-aws   { background: var(--c-aws-bg);   color: var(--c-aws);      border: 1px solid var(--c-aws-b); }
.pill-gcp   { background: var(--c-gcp-bg);   color: var(--c-gcp);      border: 1px solid var(--c-gcp-b); }
.pill-cf    { background: var(--c-cf-bg);    color: var(--c-cf);       border: 1px solid var(--c-cf-b); }
.pill-drata { background: var(--c-drata-bg); color: var(--c-drata);    border: 1px solid var(--c-drata-b); }
.pill-gh    { background: var(--c-github-bg);color: var(--c-github);   border: 1px solid var(--c-github-b); }
.pill-opt   { background: var(--c-opt-bg);   color: var(--c-optional); border: 1px solid var(--c-opt-b); }

/* ── Divider ─────────────────────────────────── */
.divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
}

/* ── Progress bar ────────────────────────────── */
.progress-bar {
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--border);
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
}

.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: #1bc47d;
  width: 0%;
  transition: width 0.1s linear;
}

/* ── Screen reader ───────────────────────────── */
.sr-only { position: absolute; width:1px; height:1px; overflow:hidden; clip:rect(0,0,0,0); }

@media (max-width: 800px) {
  .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  aside { display: none; }
  .step { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  .page-header { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress"></div></div>

<div class="layout">

<!-- ── Sidebar ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<aside>
  <div class="sidebar-brand">
    <div class="brand-label">Branch · PCI DSS v4.0</div>
    <div class="brand-title">Deployment Guide</div>
    <a href="index.html" style="font-size:0.65rem;color:#7a7570;text-decoration:none;margin-top:0.5rem;display:block;">← Back to Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <div class="sidebar-section-label">Steps</div>
  <nav id="sidebar-nav">
    <a href="#step-prereqs" class="active"><span class="step-circle">0</span>Prerequisites</a>
    <a href="#step-repo"><span class="step-circle">1</span>Create GitHub Repo</a>
    <a href="#step-aws"><span class="step-circle">2</span>AWS Setup</a>
    <a href="#step-gcp"><span class="step-circle">3</span>GCP Setup</a>
    <a href="#step-cloudflare"><span class="step-circle">4</span>Cloudflare Setup</a>
    <a href="#step-drata"><span class="step-circle">5</span>Drata Connections</a>
    <a href="#step-tfvars"><span class="step-circle">6</span>Configure Variables</a>
    <a href="#step-secrets"><span class="step-circle">7</span>GitHub Secrets</a>
    <a href="#step-push"><span class="step-circle">8</span>Push & Deploy</a>
    <a href="#step-verify"><span class="step-circle">9</span>Verify Deployment</a>
    <a href="#step-pages"><span class="step-circle">10</span>GitHub Pages</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="legend">
    <div class="legend-title">Color Key — Inputs</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-required);"></div> Required — must change</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-aws);"></div> AWS value</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-gcp);"></div> GCP value</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-cf);"></div> Cloudflare value</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-drata);"></div> Drata value</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-github);"></div> GitHub value</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--c-optional);"></div> Optional / default ok</div>
  </div>
</aside>

<!-- ── Main ────────────────────────────────────── -->
<main>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-eyebrow">Branch · PCI DSS v4.0 · Compliance as Code</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">Deployment Guide</h1>
    <p class="page-desc">Step-by-step instructions to deploy the Terraform PCI compliance project. Highlighted values indicate exactly what you need to replace — color-coded by provider.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────
       STEP 0 — Prerequisites
  ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="step" id="step-prereqs">
    <div class="step-header">
      <div class="step-num-large">0</div>
      <div class="step-title-block">
        <div class="step-phase">Before You Begin</div>
        <div class="step-title">Prerequisites &amp; Tool Versions</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="step-desc">Install and authenticate each tool before running any Terraform commands. Versions listed are minimums.</p>

    <div class="substep">
      <div class="substep-title">Required Tools</div>
      <div class="code-block">
        <div class="code-label">terminal — verify installations<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button></div>
        <pre><span class="c"># Check versions — all must pass</span>
terraform --version     <span class="c"># need >= 1.5.0</span>
aws --version           <span class="c"># need >= 2.x</span>
gcloud --version        <span class="c"># need >= 450.x</span>
git --version           <span class="c"># any recent version</span>
jq --version            <span class="c"># used in CI scripts</span></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="substep">
      <div class="substep-title">Required Accounts &amp; Access Levels</div>
      <table class="input-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Service</th><th>Access Required</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="row-aws"><td class="key">AWS</td><td class="desc">IAM user or role with <code>AdministratorAccess</code></td><td class="where">For initial setup only — Drata role uses SecurityAudit</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-gcp"><td class="key">GCP</td><td class="desc">Project Owner or roles/editor + roles/iam.admin</td><td class="where">Needed to create service accounts and Org Policies</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-cf"><td class="key">Cloudflare</td><td class="desc">Account-level API token with Zone:Edit + Firewall:Edit</td><td class="where">See Step 4 for exact token permissions</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-drata"><td class="key">Drata</td><td class="desc">Admin role</td><td class="where">Needed to create connections and obtain External ID</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-gh"><td class="key">GitHub</td><td class="desc">Repo Admin or Org Owner</td><td class="where">For creating repo, secrets, and branch protection</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="substep">
      <div class="substep-title">Authenticate each CLI</div>
      <div class="code-block">
        <div class="code-label">terminal<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button></div>
        <pre><span class="c"># AWS — configure with your credentials</span>
aws configure
<span class="c"># AWS Access Key ID: [enter yours]</span>
<span class="c"># AWS Secret Access Key: [enter yours]</span>
<span class="c"># Default region: us-east-1</span>
<span class="c"># Default output format: json</span>

<span class="c"># GCP — application default login</span>
gcloud auth application-default login
gcloud config set project <span class="i-gcp">YOUR-GCP-PROJECT-ID</span>

<span class="c"># Verify AWS identity</span>
aws sts get-caller-identity</pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────
       STEP 1 — Create GitHub Repo
  ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="step" id="step-repo">
    <div class="step-header">
      <div class="step-num-large">1</div>
      <div class="step-title-block">
        <div class="step-phase">GitHub</div>
        <div class="step-title">Create the Repository</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="step-desc">Create a private repo and push the project. The <code>docs/</code> folder will later serve the compliance dashboard via GitHub Pages.</p>

    <div class="substep">
      <div class="substep-title">Create on GitHub.com</div>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>Go to <strong>github.com/new</strong></li>
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>Repository name: <strong>pci-compliance</strong> (or your preferred name)</li>
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>Visibility: <strong>Private</strong> — this repo contains infra definitions</li>
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>Do <em>not</em> initialize with README (you'll push the existing files)</li>
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>Click <strong>Create repository</strong></li>
