git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/<span class="i-gh">YOUR-ORG</span>/<span class="i-gh">pci-compliance</span>.git
git push -u origin main</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="callout callout-warn">
        <span class="callout-icon">⚠️</span>
        <div class="callout-body">
          <strong>Never commit <code>terraform.tfvars</code></strong>
          The <code>.gitignore</code> above blocks it, but double-check with <code>git status</code> before every push. Your Cloudflare token and Drata External ID live in that file.
