    <div class="substep">
      <div class="substep-title">Enable branch protection</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:0.6rem;">Settings → Branches → Add rule → branch name pattern: <code>main</code></p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>✅ Require a pull request before merging</li>
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>✅ Require status checks to pass: <code>security-scan</code>, <code>terraform-plan</code></li>
        <li><div class="check-box"></div>✅ Require branches to be up to date before merging</li>
